flowchart TB
    N1["1. Entry domain: Solana instruction | token account state | bridge authority"]
    N2["2. Normalization: shape heterogeneous events into chain-neutral, hashable, replay-protected messages"]
    N3["3. Core mechanism: Validate route | Move escrowed assets | Emit bridge event"]
    N4["4. State and commitment: message hash, nonce, source height, and asset action"]
    N5["5. Evidence or result: bridge event | escrow mutation | relay evidence"]
    N6["6. Consumer boundary: watcher-sol | gateway | shared bridge"]
    N7["7. Failure path: insufficient confirmations, nonce replay, message mismatch, or invalid asset state"]
    N8["8. Extension point: source-chain watchers, message routes, asset mapping, and confirmation policy"]
    N1 --> N2
    N1 --> N3
    N1 --> N4
    N1 --> N5
    N1 --> N6
    N1 --> N7
    N1 --> N8
    N2 -. constrains .-> N4
    N4 -. produces .-> N5
    N5 -. consumed by .-> N6
    classDef core fill:#0f172a,stroke:#38bdf8,color:#e5f2ff,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef support fill:#111827,stroke:#64748b,color:#f8fafc;
    class N1 core;
    class N2,N3,N4,N5,N6,N7,N8 support;
